# global-news

global-news is a news aggregator written to fulfill the coding exercise for a BBC role.

## Installation

```js
npm install
```

## Development

```js
npm start
```

## Build
runs webpack in production mode and delivers bundled js and index.html to the `./dist` directory.
```js 
npm run build
```

## Run
builds and spins up python's SimpleHTTPServer, serving at [localhost:8001](localhost:8001)

```js
npm run launch
```
